snippet: Czech Jaromir Jagr became the second highest points scorer of all time in the National Hockey League (NHL) when the Florida Panthers winger collected an assist for Aleksander Barkov against the Boston Bruins on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Czech Jaromir Jagr became the second highest points scorer of all time in the National Hockey League (NHL) when the Florida Panthers winger collected an assist for Aleksander Barkov against the Boston Bruins on Thursday.

headline.main: Jagr Climbs to Second on Highest NHL Points List
headline.print_headline: Jagr Climbs to Second on Highest NHL Points List
